303
00:22:25,065 --> 00:22:27,863
I guess it sort of chooses you sometimes.

304
00:22:29,904 --> 00:22:31,838
It's more than some crush, Bella.

305
00:22:31,906 --> 00:22:34,067
Sam imprinted on Emily.

306
00:22:35,977 --> 00:22:38,172
Do I even want to know what that is?

307
00:22:47,355 --> 00:22:50,017
Imprinting on someone is like...

308
00:22:52,394 --> 00:22:54,453
Like when you see her,

309
00:22:55,730 --> 00:22:57,527
everything changes.

310
00:22:59,033 --> 00:23:02,833
All of a sudden,
it's not gravity holding you to the planet.

311
00:23:03,938 --> 00:23:05,235
It's her.

312
00:23:06,141 --> 00:23:08,006
Nothing else matters.

313
00:23:09,244 --> 00:23:11,269
You would do anything,

314
00:23:12,881 --> 00:23:14,610
